      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I have absolutely babied this car since day one, and it is still in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and honestly feels like it just rolled off the lot. I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
