    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-spec with zero subframe fatigue, benefiting from a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system and a 3.64 limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolsters are indistinguishable from showroom delivery. Mechanically synchronized and dynamically perfect, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
