      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning factory paint which retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service record with every scheduled maintenance performed strictly by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing. If you are looking for the absolute best, this is it.",
